== Setting up the Mac Mini
* Install Brew
  /usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.github.com/gist/323731)"
* Install RVM > bash < <(curl -s https://raw.github.com/wayneeseguin/rvm/master/binscripts/rvm-installer)
* Install Ruby 1.9.2-p290 (set as default)
  gem update --system
  gem install bundler
  gem install rails
  rvm use ruby-1.9.2-p290 --default
  mkdir local
  echo 'export PATH=$HOME/local/bin:$PATH' >> ~/.bashrc
* Install Redis
  brew install redis
  mkdir -p ~/Library/LaunchAgents
  cp /usr/local/Cellar/redis/2.2.14/io.redis.redis-server.plist ~/Library/LaunchAgents/
  launchctl load -w ~/Library/LaunchAgents/io.redis.redis-server.plist
  redis-cli (to test if its working)
* Install Resque
  gem install resque
* Install Foreman
  gem install foreman


* Install ImageMagick
  brew install imagemagick

OR

* Install MacPorts
  Download dmg from web
* Install libdevil
  sudo port install libdevil